```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    title Webhook Processing Flow - Assinafy to ASOF

    participant Assinafy as Assinafy API
    participant ASOF_API as ASOF Webhook Endpoint
    participant Validator as Signature Validator
    participant Queue as Job Queue
    participant DB as Database
    participant Log as Audit Log

    Assinafy->>ASOF_API: 1. POST /webhook/assinafy
    activate ASOF_API

    ASOF_API->>Validator: 2. Validate webhook signature
    activate Validator

    alt Invalid signature
        Validator-->>ASOF_API: Validation failed
        ASOF_API-->>Assinafy: 401 Unauthorized
        deactivate ASOF_API
    else Valid signature
        Validator-->>ASOF_API: Signature valid
        deactivate Validator

        ASOF_API->>ASOF_API: 3. Parse event payload
        ASOF_API->>Queue: 4. Queue async job
        activate Queue
        Queue-->>ASOF_API: job_id
        deactivate Queue

        ASOF_API-->>Assinafy: 200 OK
        deactivate ASOF_API

        Note over Queue: Async processing begins

        Queue->>DB: 5. Update document status
        activate DB
        DB-->>Queue: Success
        deactivate DB

        Queue->>Log: 6. Log webhook event
        activate Log
        Log-->>Queue: Logged
        deactivate Log

        Queue->>DB: 7. Store raw payload snapshot
        activate DB
        DB-->>Queue: Success
        deactivate DB

        alt Document is certificated
            Queue->>Queue: 8. Trigger download job
        end
    end
```
